# CoffeeToken Smart Contract

CoffeeToken is an ERC20-based token designed for a coffee shop's loyalty program. Customers earn tokens for their purchases, which they can transfer to other users or burn if they decide to leave the program. Only the contract owner (the coffee shop) has the authority to mint new tokens.

## Features

- **Minting**: Only the contract owner can mint new tokens.
- **Transferring**: Any user can transfer tokens to another user.
- **Burning**: Any user can burn their own tokens.

## Contract Details

- **Name**: CoffeeToken
- **Symbol**: COFFEE
- **Standard**: ERC20
